'''Monitor Control''' was the security center of [[Metalorn/Legends|Metalorn]] and the frequent haunt of its technology-reliant [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Governor/Legends|Governor]] [[Corwyth]]. Monitor control could control all information flow on the planet and track the location of all weaponry.

